<L>__{194c the whole lower leg shatters at the impact. it topples forward to its}
<A>__{knees. catches itself on one hand. liquid nitrogen flows around the hand. now the hand is stuck to the pavement.}
<L>__{194d the t 1000 pulls and... clink! the hand snaps off at the wrist.}
<A>__{it looks stupidly at the glassy stump of a wrist. for the first time we see an expression on its face we know to be a true one... the expression is pain. agony. its mouth opens in a soundless scream as the hoar frost races up its legs, across its body.}
